  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mistral is a fast paced action roguelike game build with replayability in mind. Explore the land of Mistral, pick relics to upgrade your character and vanquish your enemies.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique combat styles, master each weapons to your advantage !<br></li><li>Deep character upgrade system with large item selection. Strategize for your conquest !<br></li><li>Dying is not the end, unlock powers to get permanently stronger for your next run.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging gameplay and dynamic combat mechanics.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The environment settings change each time you explore the world.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/6f221c07df6e3362310e51124ebc2f24.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/6f221c07df6e3362310e51124ebc2f24.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/6f221c07df6e3362310e51124ebc2f24.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go on adventure with your friends in co-op mode (up to 8 players). Or meet news friends.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/3d05dce1a5b08b01e9ba97a52b3cf282.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/3d05dce1a5b08b01e9ba97a52b3cf282.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/3d05dce1a5b08b01e9ba97a52b3cf282.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mistral is a fast paced action roguelike game build with replayability in mind. Explore the land of Mistral, pick relics to upgrade your character and vanquish your enemies.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique combat styles, master each weapons to your advantage !<br></li><li>Deep character upgrade system with large item selection. Strategize for your conquest !<br></li><li>Dying is not the end, unlock powers to get permanently stronger for your next run.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging gameplay and dynamic combat mechanics.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The environment settings change each time you explore the world.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline pos